trans-unit.source: Use the Dynamics GP Data Migration extension to migrate customers, vendors, inventory items, and accounts from Dynamics GP to Business Central.

seg-source.mrk: Use the Dynamics GP Data Migration extension to migrate customers, vendors, inventory items, and accounts from Dynamics GP to Business Central.

target.mrk: Pomocí rozšíření Dynamics GP Migration můžete migrovat zákazníky, dodavatele, skladové položky a účty z Dynamics GP do Business Central.

trans-unit.source: The Dynamics GP Data Migration Extension for Finance and Operations, Business edition

seg-source.mrk: The Dynamics GP Data Migration Extension for Finance and Operations, Business edition

target.mrk: Rozšíření Dynamics GP Data Migration pro Finance and Operations, Business edition

trans-unit.source: This extension makes it easy to migrate customers, vendors, inventory items, and accounts from Dynamics GP to [!INCLUDE [d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: This extension makes it easy to migrate customers, vendors, inventory items, and accounts from Dynamics GP to [!INCLUDE [d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Toto rozšíření usnadňuje migraci zákazníků, dodavatelů, skladových položek a účtů z aplikace Dynamics GP do [!INCLUDE [d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: If your business uses Dynamics GP today, you can export the relevant master records and then open an assisted setup guide to add the data to [!INCLUDE [d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: If your business uses Dynamics GP today, you can export the relevant master records and then open an assisted setup guide to add the data to [!INCLUDE [d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Pokud vaše firma nyní používá aplikaci Dynamics GP, můžete exportovat příslušné hlavní záznamy a poté otevřít průvodce asistovaným nastavením pro přidání dat do [!INCLUDE [d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Importing Business Data from Other Finance Systems](across-import-data-configuration-packages.md).

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see [Importing Business Data from Other Finance Systems](across-import-data-configuration-packages.md).

target.mrk: Pro více informací navštivte [Importování obchodních dat z jiných finančních systémů.](across-import-data-configuration-packages.md)

trans-unit.source: During the process, supporting setup information is created, such as posting groups.

trans-unit.source: Inventory items will be brought into the system with FIFO as the cost valuation method.

target.mrk: Skladové položky budou do systému převedeny pomocí metody FIFO jakožto metody oceňování nákladů.

trans-unit.source: Accounts will be set up as the main account segment from Dynamics GP with dimensions, because [!INCLUDE [d365fin](includes/d365fin_long_md.md)] does not have account segments.
